<! [CDATA[
 Embracer Group Logo
Embracer Group AB is a Swedish video game holding company based in Karlstad. The company was established under the name Nordic Games in December 2008, forming the video game publishing subsidiary of game retailer Game Outlet Europe. Founders include chief executive officer and Game Outlet Europe founder Lars Wingefors and Pelle Lundborg. In 2011, Nordic Games established a second office, Nordic Games GmbH, in Vienna, Austria, and soon shifted its publishing operations to the new office.
